title: Episode 176: Planted, not buried (Feat. Ronnie & Shamari Devoe and Rico Love)
itunes:title: Episode 176: Planted, not buried (Feat. Ronnie & Shamari Devoe and Rico Love)
description:
Singers and reality stars Ronnie and Shamari Devoe as well as Producer Rico Love join the Ladies of Lip Service this week and discuss the challenges they face while being married. The Devoe's speak on their open relationship and how it almost ended their marriage, but ultimately brought them closer than ever. Enjoy!
